Package ispd.arquivo.xml.utils

Class WrappedDocument

java.lang.Object
ispd.arquivo.xml.utils.WrappedDocument
public class WrappedDocument extends Object
Utility class to add convenience methods to manipulate XML Document objects. It functions as a wrapper, outsourcing method calls to the inner object.
